criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of asthma;

          -  Age equal to or greater than 18 years;

          -  Resolved primary non-adherence;

          -  ACT score less than 20 points;

          -  Patients who can read and write;

          -  Possibility of using the WhatsApp® application (by video call)

          -  Acceptance by written or audio message, from the informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who do not attend the research team in the foreseen contacts, always in five
             attempts for each stage of the study, whether via telephone contact or video calls,
             will be excluded from the study.
